Main Features:
    1. Added Main and Small card lists/mock databases.
    2. Added mainitem.model.ts, which allows for quick creation of cards based on input image, logo, and description (main only).
    3. Added ngFor loop to iterate through mock database and push attributes to display. 
    4. Integrated data binding to main and small card html files. 
    4. Updated app.component.html to display multiple cards based off of database.

    To display ability to create multiple cards with the loop, added more smallgamecards. 